{"tid":2249487,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"爆谷店經理藏伸縮棍鐵蓮花囚8個月","createTime":"2020-10-19T11:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T11:55:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9511bf97a47c083991733023529027eaeaa8821d","tid":2249487,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:09:17.000Z","msg":"爆谷店經理去年8月底在上水遭警員埋伏截查，在其背囊中搜出懷疑伸縮棍及摺刀，凌晨時分又在其家中搜出兩個「鐵蓮花」等物。被告早前承認一項管有違禁武器、即兩個鐵蓮花，但否認一項管有攻擊性武器罪，經審訊後罪名成立，今共被判囚8個月。<br />\n<br />\n暫委裁判官莊靜慧今就管有攻擊性武器罪名判囚8個月，管有違禁武器則判囚2個月。兩項控罪同期執行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/WAUVH5RNHFBPRG2JSBI5CSZRIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FWAUVH5RNHFBPRG2JSBI5CSZRIE%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZtjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=50ec7386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FWAUVH5RNHFBPRG2JSBI5CSZRIE%2F&h=c511b28d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/WAUVH5RNHFBPRG2JSBI5CSZRIE/</a>"},{"pid":"db66c1a131fc1fb82988bc7d7f98c1a96d11e337","tid":2249487,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f402be95e913cced9eb745f3b357e54d3eaa736","tid":2249487,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415905c9f02fd1bf2ed641beb925adf492f0b126","tid":2249487,"uid":194363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6997bdc3edd454421c69e076d85490650e6e1166","tid":2249487,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:52:23.000Z","msg":"莊靜慧"},{"pid":"419967bed8102f09a48735a527966ffdf41f57bc","t